comment.body:
Running into an error after pressing the 'Join the DAO' button. because of an undefined backgroundColor prop not being passed to the NewProposal.js Component

I included after line 41 -
```
    const { dao, backgroundColor } = this.props.navigation.state.params;
    this.props.navigation.navigate('DAOstack/NewProposal', { dao, backgroundColor });
```
 - and it fixed the error.

Nice touch with the background color change for the header to match the DAO!
